data.description: Nestled in East Detroit, this charming ranch has undergone a stunning renovation, making it a true gem, it presents an enticing opportunity for investors seeking to expand their portfolios with an exceptional ROI or First Time Buyer’s . Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, a spacious basement, and a 2-car garage, it offers both comfort and practicality. Don't miss out on this investment opportunity where beauty meets profitability!
